In a message dated 7/31/03 12:47:23 AM Central Daylight Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "What's wrong??, my dear MAxima?"  said Hydras

Still being repaired, she looked up at Hydras. usually she would keep secrets 
from others. But not him. She couldn't keep a secret from him. How could 
she... he was still Megatron. She would give her very existance for him. 

Recomposing herself. "I.. was given an .. object. Which I now carry. Given to 
me for safe keeping." in a softer tone. "no one else must know I have it." 
she looked at him with a slight concern, not sure how he would react to it. "I 
was told it was a dormant Decepticon Matrix." Somehow, it was not so dormant. 
It seemed to be attatching itself to her. 

Her repairs soon enough was nearly complete. 

--part1_105.33ad748c.2c5a0c1c_boundary
